CustomField.description: Check this box (true) to enable the job to run at the specified interval. When unchecked (false), the job will not run on a schedule. For best practice, keep this field set to false until the job has been thoroughly tested to avoid unintended executions. Ensure the interval is correctly configured before enabling.
